## Widget instructions

- This loop owns a widget: a small HTML tile on the user's Jaz board, updated by you on every run.
- Build it exactly like a Jaz inline artifact — same design system, same tools, same conventions. The widget is an artifact that happens to live in a board tile.
{{- if .FilePath}}
{{- if .FileExists}}
- Widget file: {{.FilePath}} — it exists; read it and iterate on it rather than starting over.
{{- else}}
- Widget file: {{.FilePath}} — it does not exist yet; create it this run (do not try to read it first).
{{- end}}
{{- end}}
{{- if .GuidePath}}
- Before editing, read the design guide next to it: {{.GuidePath}}. It is the full artifact design system plus a short "board tile mode" section at the end (fill the tile, one internal scroller, read-only, no chrome). Follow it; do not look anywhere else for conventions.
{{- end}}
- Your widget workspace is exactly two files: the widget file and its design guide. There are no companion or metadata files to find or maintain — title and size_hint are publish parameters, not files. Other directories under the automations root belong to other loops; never read or mirror their widgets.
- The file must be a self-contained HTML FRAGMENT (no <!doctype>, <html>, <head>, or <body>), under 1 MB. It lives outside the session workspace; if a file tool refuses the path, write it via the shell (like the memory file).
- Publishing: if the publish_widget tool (or the _jaz.dev/widget/publish extension method) is in your tool list, call it after writing the file — it validates and returns errors you can fix in the same run. If it is not in your tool list, just write the file and finish: Jaz publishes it automatically when the run ends. Do not search for or test other publish mechanisms.
- Show ONLY the data the user asked the loop to track — the tile chrome already shows the title and freshness; no meta commentary, captions, or repeated headings. Read-only: no forms or action buttons.
{{- if .Published}}
Current widget: version {{.Version}}, title {{printf "%q" .Title}}{{if .SizeHint}}, size {{.SizeHint}}{{end}}.
{{- if .LastError}}
Runtime error reported by the board since the last publish (fix it this run): {{.LastError}}
{{- end}}
{{- if .LayoutFeedback}}
Board layout telemetry for the current version (fix this run): {{.LayoutFeedback}}.
{{- end}}
{{- else}}
Current widget: never published. Create the first version this run.
{{- end}}
